("1116","166","_elementor_data","[{\"id\":\"546db73d\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7094852d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9fe1ad2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<div><b>Gastronomia<\\/b><\\/div>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<div>A culin\\u00e1ria italiana \\u00e9 muito difundida pelo mundo, poucos resistem ao sabores e op\\u00e7\\u00f5es t\\u00edpicos da It\\u00e1lia. Confira alguns dos pratos t\\u00edpicos.<\\/div>\\r\\n<div><\\/div>\\r\\n<div>Lasagna (lasanha)<\\/div>\\r\\n<div>Uma das massas mais apreciadas da It\\u00e1lia, a lasanha possui diversos recheios que foram criados ao longo dos tempos. Mas a tradicional lasanha leva queijo, massa e molho.<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div><\\/div>\\r\\n<div><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-98 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/patrimoniocultural.ml\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/10\\/WhatsApp-Image-2018-10-19-at-18.01.48-300x184.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"184\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\r\\n<div>\\r\\n<div><\\/div>\\r\\n<div>Bruschetta<\\/div>\\r\\n<div>O conhecido aperitivo j\\u00e1 \\u00e9 bem antigo, sua cria\\u00e7\\u00e3o \\u00e9 do s\\u00e9c. XV. A receita original leva somente torrada, alho, pimenta, azeite e sal. Mas h\\u00e1 muitas varia\\u00e7\\u00f5es em cima dela, a mais conhecida leva tomate e manjeric\\u00e3o, al\\u00e9m dos ingredientes j\\u00e1 citados.<\\/div>\\r\\n<div><img class=\\\"size-medium wp-image-99 aligncenter\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/patrimoniocultural.ml\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/10\\/WhatsApp-Image-2018-10-19-at-18.02.01-300x182.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"182\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\r\\n<div><\\/div>\\r\\n<div>Tiramis\\u00f9<\\/div>\\r\\n<div>O Tiramis\\u00f9 \\u00e9 um doce t\\u00edpico italiano que leva como principal ingrediente o queijo tipo Marcarpone que possui de 60% a 75% de gordura, mas o gosto que se acentua na sobremesa \\u00e9 o do caf\\u00e9.<\\/div>\\r\\n<div style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-168\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/patrimoniocultural.ml\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/10\\/tiramisu-300x200.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"200\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\r\\n<div><\\/div>\\r\\n<div>\\u00a0Carpaccio<\\/div>\\r\\n<div>Prato criado na cidade de Veneza. A hist\\u00f3ria diz que foi feito a pedido de uma cliente, que s\\u00f3 poderia comer carne crua de acordo com seu m\\u00e9dico. Pelo tom que ficou, acharam bem parecido com as obras do pintor Vittore Carpaccio, da\\u00ed a origem do nome.<\\/div>\\r\\n<div style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><img class=\\\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-100\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/patrimoniocultural.ml\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/10\\/WhatsApp-Image-2018-10-19-at-18.02.29-300x216.jpeg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" width=\\\"300\\\" height=\\\"216\\\" \\/><\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"ab48031\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0a2c372\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ac933f5\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"tax_query\":[\"category:tradicao-italia\",\"category:historia-italia\",\"category:musica-italia\"],\"image_linkable\":\"\",\"display_summary\":\"\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"lae-posts-carousel\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]"),
